<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "BostonrbExamples" %></title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML elements -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all" %>

    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon-72x72.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72">
    <link href="images/apple-touch-icon-114x114.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114">
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="navbar-inner">
        <div class="container">
          <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-target=".nav-collapse" data-toggle="collapse">
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </a>
          <a class="brand" href="#">Boston Ruby Group - Donations Counter Example</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="row">
           <div class="span9">
              <%= yield %>
            </div>
            <div class="span3">
              <div class="well sidebar-nav">
                <p>This website is an example application designed to give new rails developers 
                  a sandbox with some exercises to try.  The layout is courtesy of the 
                  <a href="https://github.com/seyhunak/twitter-bootstrap-rails">twitter-bootstrap-rails gem</a>, 
                  and the application is designed to be deployed to <a href="http://www.heroku.com/">heroku</a>.</p>
                <p>Follow along with the exercises described in the README or at the 
                  <a href="https://github.com/dylancashman/bostonrb-examples">github page</a>.</p>
              </div><!--/.well -->
            </div><!--/span-->
        </div><!--/row-->
      </div><!--/content-->

      <footer>
        <p>Page developed by <a href="http://bostonrb.org/">Boston Ruby Group</p>
      </footer>

    </div> <!-- /container -->

    <!-- Javascripts
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>

  </body>
</html>
